WEBVTT

00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:03.406
(Previously) There's a new cat café
nearby. They post promo clips nonstop.

00:00:03.587 --> 00:00:05.726
We need to do promo clips to fight back.

00:00:06.006 --> 00:00:08.627
Are you two the owners of Cat-Cheer Café?

00:00:08.759 --> 00:00:10.027
We've been watching
your clips on loop all day.

00:00:10.051 --> 00:00:11.093
So swoon-worthy!

00:00:11.232 --> 00:00:13.726
You two really look like
a couple getting married.

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:15.520
I asked them to sell this to me.

00:00:15.813 --> 00:00:18.120
I'd like to put this ring on you.

00:00:19.779 --> 00:00:21.159
Who's left?

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:23.713
Do you want to meet my parents?

00:00:26.187 --> 00:00:29.506
Help me with these glasses. Come on.

00:00:29.587 --> 00:00:30.587
Oi.

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:39.420
(Mommy, are you okay?)

00:00:41.427 --> 00:00:43.913
We're both really old now, Granny Juu.

00:00:44.313 --> 00:00:47.640
It's almost time to pass this power on.

00:00:47.833 --> 00:00:51.613
(And have you decided
who you'll pass it on to?)

00:00:59.946 --> 00:01:00.946
That's a tough one.

00:01:07.599 --> 00:01:11.596
But if I had to pass it on,
it'd have to be…

00:01:23.117 --> 00:01:24.117
What's that?

00:01:26.101 --> 00:01:27.101
Isn't it pretty?

00:01:27.160 --> 00:01:28.811
It's your photo from the fashion show.

00:01:29.172 --> 00:01:30.388
It was delivered this morning.

00:01:31.205 --> 00:01:32.620
Why did you hang it up there?

00:01:32.892 --> 00:01:34.267
It looks like a pre-wedding photo.

00:01:34.292 --> 00:01:35.292
It's embarrassing.

00:01:35.372 --> 00:01:36.861
What's there to be embarrassed about?

00:01:36.999 --> 00:01:39.618
You've got something good,
let the world know it's yours.

00:01:41.914 --> 00:01:44.048
Where are you taking Granny Juu?

00:01:45.390 --> 00:01:46.908
She hasn't been eating much lately,

00:01:46.933 --> 00:01:48.278
so I'm taking her to see Dr. Pom.

00:01:51.054 --> 00:01:54.097
Dr. Pom isn't in today, only Dr. Pug is.

00:01:54.353 --> 00:01:55.406
I'll take her there for you.

00:01:55.430 --> 00:01:56.430
Wait.

00:01:56.894 --> 00:01:58.616
How do you even know who's in
and who isn't?

00:02:00.104 --> 00:02:01.104
You don't need to know.

00:02:35.643 --> 00:02:38.004
Cat-Cheer Café, welcome.

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:42.360
Hi there.

00:02:45.311 --> 00:02:46.326
Can I get a coffee?

00:03:41.300 --> 00:03:43.300
"Cat for Cash"
(Episode 10)

00:03:46.020 --> 00:03:46.942
Here's your Americano.

00:03:47.011 --> 00:03:48.297
Oh, thank you.

00:03:50.238 --> 00:03:52.607
I had some errands nearby,

00:03:53.108 --> 00:03:55.608
and I just found out
there's a café like this around here.

00:03:55.826 --> 00:03:58.597
I actually took it over from my mom.

00:03:58.930 --> 00:04:00.103
She's a big cat lover.

00:04:00.174 --> 00:04:01.901
I like cats too, but…

00:04:02.479 --> 00:04:03.895
my son's allergic to cats,

00:04:04.423 --> 00:04:05.798
so I could never keep one at home.

00:04:06.307 --> 00:04:07.337
Same with my partner.

00:04:08.093 --> 00:04:11.404
He likes cats too, but he's allergic.

00:04:11.807 --> 00:04:13.613
So the most he can do is
help me run the café.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:17.612
Wow, even with the allergy,
he still helps you out.

00:04:18.168 --> 00:04:21.116
Tell me, where did you find
such a good partner like that?

00:04:21.290 --> 00:04:23.008
I guess he just really loves cats.

00:04:23.135 --> 00:04:24.815
Come teach my son too.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.307
He's almost 30

00:04:26.922 --> 00:04:29.516
and hasn't brought
anyone home to meet me.

00:04:30.477 --> 00:04:31.911
He's quite the catch too, you know.

00:04:32.027 --> 00:04:33.901
Let me show you his picture.

00:04:35.806 --> 00:04:36.806
Jumbo!

00:04:37.550 --> 00:04:38.441
I'm so sorry about him.

00:04:38.466 --> 00:04:39.466
It's okay.

00:04:40.993 --> 00:04:43.085
He's so playful, just like
my son when he was little.

00:04:44.425 --> 00:04:45.425
Oh!

00:04:47.696 --> 00:04:49.113
His whisker fell out.

00:04:50.153 --> 00:04:52.667
My mom said
if a cat leaves you its whisker,

00:04:52.718 --> 00:04:54.804
it means good luck.

00:04:55.621 --> 00:04:56.463
How so?

00:04:56.524 --> 00:05:00.820
You can make a wish,
and it'll come true.

00:05:01.809 --> 00:05:03.392
Do you have a wish to make?

00:05:07.377 --> 00:05:08.377
A wish?

00:05:09.806 --> 00:05:11.918
I only have one wish left in this life.

00:05:14.477 --> 00:05:17.912
I just want my son to
settle down with someone.

00:05:19.996 --> 00:05:22.196
This mother can't wait
to hold a grandchild in her arms.

00:05:22.241 --> 00:05:23.913
Sadhu.

00:05:30.028 --> 00:05:32.018
You said Granny Juu was sick,

00:05:32.718 --> 00:05:34.970
but when she got there, she was
running around like nothing was wrong.

00:05:34.994 --> 00:05:36.101
What a waste of time.

00:05:36.700 --> 00:05:37.700
Really?

00:05:38.707 --> 00:05:40.511
Then why do you look so happy?

00:05:42.337 --> 00:05:43.343
You can tell?

00:05:45.084 --> 00:05:49.024
The vet wants to schedule another checkup.

00:05:50.392 --> 00:05:52.598
Maybe he's just looking for an excuse
to see me again.

00:05:52.851 --> 00:05:53.971
Don't get ahead of yourself.

00:05:54.090 --> 00:05:55.694
He was probably just doing his job.

00:05:57.502 --> 00:05:58.793
Don't be jealous.

00:06:00.491 --> 00:06:02.807
Hey, your man's here.

00:06:03.788 --> 00:06:04.722
I should get going.

00:06:04.811 --> 00:06:06.142
I don't want to be a third wheel.

00:06:08.439 --> 00:06:09.559
How was today?

00:06:11.031 --> 00:06:13.008
You don't even have to ask.
Exhausting, of course.

00:06:13.597 --> 00:06:15.401
My boyfriend left me
to run the place alone.

00:06:16.981 --> 00:06:17.981
Sorry.

00:06:19.056 --> 00:06:20.507
I had something to deal with today.

00:06:20.986 --> 00:06:24.017
I also went to see my dad
and helped him clear up his work for you.

00:06:25.309 --> 00:06:26.706
What does that have to do with me?

00:06:27.096 --> 00:06:29.498
I told you I wanted to
introduce you to my mom.

00:06:29.916 --> 00:06:32.823
But my dad got held up with work,

00:06:33.358 --> 00:06:34.993
so I helped finish it.

00:06:35.283 --> 00:06:38.914
In return, I get to bring you
to meet them tomorrow.

00:06:39.020 --> 00:06:40.020
Tomorrow?

00:06:44.096 --> 00:06:45.110
Isn't that too soon?

00:06:45.828 --> 00:06:46.828
Not at all.

00:06:47.418 --> 00:06:48.804
Let's just go meet my mom

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:50.503
before she starts coming after me.

00:06:52.213 --> 00:06:54.202
I can't wait to introduce you to them.

00:07:00.074 --> 00:07:01.074
Ahem.

00:07:04.782 --> 00:07:06.008
Ugh, so annoying.

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.013
People in love stink.

00:07:16.215 --> 00:07:18.112
Have you ever introduced anyone
to your parents?

00:07:20.822 --> 00:07:23.911
No. You're the first one.

00:07:25.259 --> 00:07:26.282
Why do you ask?

00:07:30.725 --> 00:07:33.321
As for my mom…

00:07:33.810 --> 00:07:35.415
she kind of knows my type,

00:07:35.909 --> 00:07:37.029
my preference.

00:07:40.798 --> 00:07:41.815
What about your family?

00:07:44.306 --> 00:07:45.505
As for that,

00:07:46.850 --> 00:07:48.113
my dad already knows.

00:07:48.830 --> 00:07:50.393
My mom doesn't know yet.

00:07:52.100 --> 00:07:53.695
But I think she should be okay with it.

00:08:06.142 --> 00:08:08.115
Granny Juu once left me
one of her whiskers.

00:08:08.778 --> 00:08:10.511
They say you can make a wish with it.

00:08:11.070 --> 00:08:12.210
Do you think we…

00:08:12.876 --> 00:08:14.687
should wish for your mom to accept us?

00:08:17.153 --> 00:08:18.297
You don't need to.

00:08:19.170 --> 00:08:20.170
I'm sure

00:08:22.117 --> 00:08:25.904
my mom and dad will like you.

00:08:29.571 --> 00:08:30.604
Even I…

00:08:33.059 --> 00:08:34.059
like you.

00:09:07.582 --> 00:09:09.217
This is my dad.

00:09:09.801 --> 00:09:10.660
Hello.

00:09:10.787 --> 00:09:11.787
Hello.

00:09:13.406 --> 00:09:14.516
Don't be nervous.

00:09:15.361 --> 00:09:18.802
My wife may look a bit intimidating,

00:09:19.135 --> 00:09:20.513
but actually…

00:09:21.666 --> 00:09:22.731
she's really intimidating.

00:09:24.846 --> 00:09:25.846
Ahem.

00:09:25.967 --> 00:09:26.967
Honey.

00:09:30.056 --> 00:09:31.056
Oh!

00:09:34.824 --> 00:09:36.408
You're the one from the cat café.

00:09:37.272 --> 00:09:38.123
Hi, ma'am.

00:09:38.166 --> 00:09:39.166
Hi.

00:09:42.408 --> 00:09:43.813
You know Lynx too, Ma?

00:09:58.442 --> 00:10:02.223
At first, I thought Tiger was introducing
his date to us.

00:10:02.746 --> 00:10:04.513
Turns out it's you, Lynx.

00:10:10.738 --> 00:10:12.797
So how did you two become friends?

00:10:17.731 --> 00:10:18.731
Ma,

00:10:19.706 --> 00:10:20.706
actually…

00:10:21.464 --> 00:10:23.458
Lynx and I are…

00:10:23.548 --> 00:10:25.100
We met at a seminar.

00:10:25.822 --> 00:10:28.904
Tiger wanted to open a coffeeshop,

00:10:29.404 --> 00:10:31.217
so he asked me to be his business partner.

00:10:45.021 --> 00:10:46.021
Lynx.

00:10:46.466 --> 00:10:48.113
Why did you lie to my mom like that?

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:51.716
Your mom wouldn't be happy

00:10:52.484 --> 00:10:54.206
if she knew I was your boyfriend.

00:10:55.446 --> 00:10:56.446
Why not?

00:10:56.962 --> 00:10:58.316
She seemed to like you.

00:10:59.388 --> 00:11:02.795
Well, she wants Tiger to have someone

00:11:03.628 --> 00:11:05.321
because she wants a grandchild.

00:11:06.759 --> 00:11:08.393
I don't want to ruin that dream of hers.

00:11:10.325 --> 00:11:11.508
What about our dream?

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:17.505
Are you really OK
with what you just did?

00:11:22.903 --> 00:11:24.311
Hey, come on.

00:11:25.615 --> 00:11:27.317
We can figure that out later.

00:11:29.129 --> 00:11:30.129
Lynx,

00:11:30.395 --> 00:11:32.122
have you ever seen
Tiger's childhood photos?

00:11:35.547 --> 00:11:37.000
Is this really the time, Pa?

00:11:37.813 --> 00:11:39.713
Here. Take a look.

00:11:45.664 --> 00:11:47.626
You weren't allergic to cats
when you were little?

00:11:48.019 --> 00:11:49.019
No.

00:11:49.874 --> 00:11:53.808
Back then, I'd run up to pet any cat I saw.

00:11:55.728 --> 00:11:57.605
Then one day my eyes
suddenly started itching.

00:11:59.090 --> 00:12:03.326
After that, even feeding a stray
would get me scolded by my mom.

00:12:05.878 --> 00:12:11.416
Tiger's condition
made my wife blame herself.

00:12:12.611 --> 00:12:14.717
She thinks it's because we had him late.

00:12:16.890 --> 00:12:18.798
Before Tiger came along,

00:12:19.894 --> 00:12:21.618
we tried for a long time.

00:12:22.418 --> 00:12:23.428
Every famous doctor,

00:12:23.453 --> 00:12:25.200
every temple people recommended
for praying, we tried them all.

00:12:25.224 --> 00:12:28.016
That's why she wants Tiger
to have a child as early as possible,

00:12:28.483 --> 00:12:31.724
so he won't carry the same guilt we did.

00:12:34.357 --> 00:12:36.147
Just give her some time.

00:12:38.073 --> 00:12:39.526
I'll help you out too.

00:12:40.044 --> 00:12:41.044
Okay?

00:12:52.232 --> 00:12:53.315
Good thing you're back.

00:12:53.622 --> 00:12:55.697
I don't know what's gotten
into your son today.

00:12:55.759 --> 00:12:56.933
He's been acting out all day.

00:12:57.260 --> 00:12:59.146
He even knocked over
the other cats' food bowls.

00:13:01.346 --> 00:13:02.346
Really?

00:13:02.931 --> 00:13:04.413
No matter how playful Jumbo gets,

00:13:04.734 --> 00:13:06.513
he's never messed with
the older cats before.

00:13:07.872 --> 00:13:08.992
Yeah, strange.

00:13:09.526 --> 00:13:10.526
Hey, Jumbo.

00:13:12.482 --> 00:13:14.203
You didn't do that, did you?

00:13:14.287 --> 00:13:17.388
(Here comes something refreshing for you!)

00:13:17.961 --> 00:13:18.961
Jumbo!

00:13:21.863 --> 00:13:23.198
Your turn to deal with him now.

00:13:24.209 --> 00:13:25.408
I've got plans with friends.

00:13:25.798 --> 00:13:28.003
I'm not coming back tonight.

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:37.424
What kind of day is this?

00:13:47.430 --> 00:13:48.828
It's the day Leo's not home.

00:13:51.389 --> 00:13:52.726
Want someone to scrub your back?

00:13:58.893 --> 00:13:59.893
I'm sorry…

00:14:01.168 --> 00:14:02.526
for lying to your mom.

00:14:05.127 --> 00:14:06.130
It's okay.

00:14:06.833 --> 00:14:09.210
You only did that because
you cared about my mom's feelings.

00:14:12.468 --> 00:14:14.503
Alright. My turn now.

00:14:24.336 --> 00:14:26.911
You know the back

00:14:29.118 --> 00:14:31.208
is one of the favorite
spots of a cat to be touched.

00:14:34.897 --> 00:14:36.014
And do you know…

00:14:39.757 --> 00:14:40.757
where else?

00:14:45.143 --> 00:14:46.143
Where?

00:14:50.476 --> 00:14:51.715
You should've told me earlier.

00:14:52.008 --> 00:14:53.448
I didn't have to bother going there.

00:14:53.524 --> 00:14:54.588
Alright, fine.

00:15:00.776 --> 00:15:01.924
Lynx's showering?

00:15:19.694 --> 00:15:21.016
Can I sleep here tonight?

00:15:27.135 --> 00:15:28.135
Please.

00:15:28.867 --> 00:15:30.570
Let me sleep here.

00:15:31.768 --> 00:15:32.768
Mm.

00:15:34.397 --> 00:15:36.106
I want to talk to you about Jumbo too.

00:15:36.542 --> 00:15:37.998
I don't know what's gotten into him.

00:15:38.193 --> 00:15:39.330
He's been acting out lately.

00:15:43.094 --> 00:15:44.711
I think it's probably…

00:15:44.856 --> 00:15:45.856
karma.

00:15:47.614 --> 00:15:49.346
When I was a teenager,
I gave my mom quite a hard time too.

00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:50.370
Hey.

00:15:50.587 --> 00:15:52.208
Don't compare my son to you.

00:15:52.985 --> 00:15:54.220
Jumbo is way cuter.

00:15:55.456 --> 00:15:56.456
Hey, Lynx.

00:15:57.597 --> 00:15:58.821
Do you realize

00:15:59.438 --> 00:16:01.506
you take the kids' side
more than mine now?

00:16:05.546 --> 00:16:06.607
That's not true.

00:16:10.002 --> 00:16:11.442
If you can change,

00:16:13.199 --> 00:16:14.486
I'll try my best to change too.

00:16:24.933 --> 00:16:25.933
I'm sorry

00:16:26.454 --> 00:16:28.271
for leaving you to run
the café alone lately.

00:16:28.505 --> 00:16:30.305
I've been getting
treatment for my allergies.

00:16:30.394 --> 00:16:31.800
It might take a while,

00:16:32.405 --> 00:16:33.405
but one day

00:16:35.289 --> 00:16:37.306
I'll be able to hold our
kids in my own arms.

00:16:40.419 --> 00:16:41.497
Until that day,

00:16:43.509 --> 00:16:45.520
touch this cat for the time being.

00:16:48.990 --> 00:16:50.350
Besides touching,

00:16:51.432 --> 00:16:52.964
can I play with this cat's belly too?

00:16:53.244 --> 00:16:54.244
Ouch!

00:17:03.361 --> 00:17:04.185
Wow.

00:17:04.223 --> 00:17:07.487
The boss lady is making fish maw soup
herself today.

00:17:09.260 --> 00:17:10.816
Did you win the lottery or something?

00:17:13.060 --> 00:17:14.098
No, I lost.

00:17:15.654 --> 00:17:16.717
I just felt like eating it.

00:17:16.741 --> 00:17:19.208
And I want to bring some to Lynx too.

00:17:20.370 --> 00:17:24.004
I've never seen you cook
for any of Tiger's friends before.

00:17:27.102 --> 00:17:28.602
Come on. Look at his friends.

00:17:29.002 --> 00:17:30.656
They're either heavy
drinkers or womanizers.

00:17:30.680 --> 00:17:31.917
Not a decent one among them.

00:17:34.094 --> 00:17:37.110
So what do you think of Lynx?

00:17:37.730 --> 00:17:40.522
Do you think he's suitable
to be Tiger's partner?

00:17:43.185 --> 00:17:47.168
Honestly, I've only met him a few times.

00:17:47.201 --> 00:17:50.800
But I don't know why,
I just really like that kid.

00:17:53.708 --> 00:17:54.717
Why are you smiling?

00:17:55.888 --> 00:17:59.000
I'm just happy for Tiger.

00:17:59.211 --> 00:18:01.406
He found a business partner
his mother likes.

00:18:24.485 --> 00:18:25.485
Jumbo!

00:18:28.091 --> 00:18:29.894
How many times have I told you
not to do that?

00:18:30.094 --> 00:18:31.577
You're so close to getting punished.

00:18:45.196 --> 00:18:46.317
Lynx's not here today?

00:18:48.452 --> 00:18:49.452
Oh!

00:19:05.295 --> 00:19:07.103
I like cats too, but…

00:19:07.626 --> 00:19:09.103
my son's allergic to cats,

00:19:09.490 --> 00:19:10.653
so I could never keep one at home.

00:19:10.677 --> 00:19:11.917
Same with my partner.

00:19:12.686 --> 00:19:14.005
He likes cats too, but he's allergic.

00:19:14.029 --> 00:19:18.221
So the most he can do is
help me run the café.

00:19:18.415 --> 00:19:22.213
At first, I thought Tiger was introducing
his date to us.

00:19:22.693 --> 00:19:24.373
Turns out it's you, Lynx.

00:19:24.550 --> 00:19:26.404
So how did you two become friends?

00:19:57.465 --> 00:19:59.325
No. I just got here.

00:20:06.678 --> 00:20:07.678
Yes, Pa?

00:20:09.581 --> 00:20:10.718
Ma came to the café?

00:20:12.226 --> 00:20:13.298
No, I haven't seen her.

00:20:15.279 --> 00:20:16.279
Okay.

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:24.240
I think…

00:20:26.447 --> 00:20:28.900
your mom knows about us now.

00:21:21.386 --> 00:21:23.906
Honey, what are you doing?

00:21:31.233 --> 00:21:33.498
Lynx is Tiger's boyfriend.

00:21:40.852 --> 00:21:42.594
You already knew?

00:21:42.989 --> 00:21:45.310
Why did everyone team up to lie to me?

00:21:46.858 --> 00:21:47.858
I'm sorry.

00:21:48.516 --> 00:21:53.813
We only did it because
we were worried about your feelings.

00:21:55.792 --> 00:21:58.592
We all know how much
you want a grandchild.

00:22:21.989 --> 00:22:22.989
Muah muah

00:22:24.479 --> 00:22:26.159
Tiger, eat your veggies.

00:22:26.184 --> 00:22:27.295
They're good for you.

00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:31.135
Come on, try them.

00:22:32.779 --> 00:22:34.195
Honey, isn't he amazing?

00:22:37.129 --> 00:22:39.373
My goodness!

00:22:39.434 --> 00:22:40.421
Come on, Tiger. Dry yourself first.

00:22:40.446 --> 00:22:42.332
Why is he like this, honey?

00:22:42.727 --> 00:22:44.814
Papa, come play in the water with me.

00:22:44.844 --> 00:22:46.410
Don't ask him to join you.

00:22:46.719 --> 00:22:48.918
Ma, can I watch this cartoon?

00:22:50.803 --> 00:22:52.104
This again?

00:22:52.171 --> 00:22:53.959
You watch it every day.
Aren't you bored of it yet?

00:22:53.983 --> 00:22:55.103
Can I? Please.

00:22:55.322 --> 00:22:56.387
I'll play it for you.

00:22:56.686 --> 00:22:58.054
Yay!

00:23:03.282 --> 00:23:04.695
Happy Mother's Day.

00:23:04.757 --> 00:23:08.124
Yes? Happy Mother's Day.

00:23:12.394 --> 00:23:13.487
Thank you so much, dear.

00:23:14.468 --> 00:23:15.668
I love you, Ma.

00:23:15.889 --> 00:23:17.224
I love you too.

00:23:17.791 --> 00:23:19.058
My son's the best.

00:23:28.217 --> 00:23:29.315
Did you know, honey?

00:23:30.148 --> 00:23:32.630
The happiest day of my life

00:23:34.593 --> 00:23:37.607
was the day I held Tiger
in my arms for the first time.

00:23:41.752 --> 00:23:42.752
Even now…

00:23:43.644 --> 00:23:45.218
I can still remember that feeling.

00:23:47.789 --> 00:23:50.327
Don't you think our son is happy now?

00:23:52.018 --> 00:23:53.018
Listen.

00:23:53.803 --> 00:23:59.014
I've never seen Tiger's eyes sparkle
the way they do when he's with Lynx.

00:24:03.285 --> 00:24:09.610
Families in their time and ours
may not look the same.

00:24:11.193 --> 00:24:13.130
But it's still a family.

00:24:16.607 --> 00:24:20.710
And our son is waiting for us
to accept his family now.

00:24:34.144 --> 00:24:35.144
Hey, Tiger.

00:24:35.793 --> 00:24:38.017
I just took Granny Juu to see the vet.

00:24:43.979 --> 00:24:45.023
Is everything alright?

00:24:48.022 --> 00:24:53.117
My mom found out
Lynx and I are together.

00:24:55.051 --> 00:24:57.001
So, is she okay with that?

00:24:59.601 --> 00:25:00.806
I can't get hold of her yet.

00:25:06.155 --> 00:25:07.155
Yes, Pa?

00:25:08.651 --> 00:25:09.651
You met Ma?

00:25:11.683 --> 00:25:12.683
Okay.

00:25:13.098 --> 00:25:14.201
Take care of her for me.

00:25:15.561 --> 00:25:16.561
Thank you.

00:25:20.211 --> 00:25:21.250
That's a relief.

00:25:21.690 --> 00:25:22.721
I'm happy for you.

00:25:24.025 --> 00:25:27.312
By the way,
what were you saying earlier?

00:25:29.346 --> 00:25:34.115
Oh, forget it.
It's nothing important.

00:25:35.751 --> 00:25:37.405
You should go be with Lynx.

00:25:37.804 --> 00:25:39.578
He's probably been overthinking it by now.

00:25:42.301 --> 00:25:43.301
Okay.

00:25:54.089 --> 00:25:55.608
My dad already talked to my mom.

00:25:56.218 --> 00:25:58.208
It's okay now.
You don't have to worry about it.

00:26:03.906 --> 00:26:04.906
I'm sorry.

00:26:10.207 --> 00:26:11.515
Stop blaming yourself.

00:26:12.039 --> 00:26:13.696
She was going to find out
sooner or later.

00:26:14.108 --> 00:26:16.107
But she should have heard it from us.

00:26:18.672 --> 00:26:20.121
I shouldn't have lied to her.

00:26:23.481 --> 00:26:24.481
It's okay.

00:26:33.387 --> 00:26:34.387
Jumbo!

00:26:37.066 --> 00:26:39.017
Didn't Papa warn you not to do that?

00:26:39.162 --> 00:26:40.376
Papa is really going to
punish you this time.

00:26:40.400 --> 00:26:42.536
(Let go of Jumbo. Put Jumbo down!)

00:26:42.570 --> 00:26:43.570
Lynx.

00:26:45.379 --> 00:26:46.127
Lynx!

00:26:46.183 --> 00:26:50.902
(Let Jumbo out! Dad, help me!)

00:26:50.936 --> 00:26:51.936
Lynx.

00:26:52.684 --> 00:26:53.814
Isn't that a bit too harsh?

00:26:53.948 --> 00:26:55.107
I read it online.

00:26:55.285 --> 00:26:57.503
They say if a cat misbehaves,
you should do this.

00:26:59.087 --> 00:27:01.710
Jumbo, if you keep acting like this,

00:27:02.484 --> 00:27:03.964
Papa won't let you stay here anymore.

00:27:04.044 --> 00:27:06.997
(Of course!
(Papa and Dad are together now.)

00:27:07.275 --> 00:27:08.892
(You don't need Jumbo anymore.)

00:27:08.998 --> 00:27:10.098
(And Bro Jiro too.)

00:27:10.193 --> 00:27:13.297
(Ever since he got a sweetheart,
he doesn't play with me anymore.)

00:27:13.404 --> 00:27:15.186
(Everyone leaves me.)

00:27:19.448 --> 00:27:20.448
Hey, Jumbo.

00:27:22.007 --> 00:27:24.914
So this is why you've been acting out?

00:27:27.487 --> 00:27:28.508
Who are you talking to?

00:27:30.383 --> 00:27:34.915
(Go on, just abandon me.
(No one loves me here anyway.)

00:27:35.016 --> 00:27:36.816
No one's gonna abandon you.

00:27:37.913 --> 00:27:42.113
Even if we have partners,
we still love you the same.

00:27:43.421 --> 00:27:47.403
If you don't believe me,
you can ask the older cats.

00:27:47.615 --> 00:27:49.993
(That's right. We're all one family.)

00:27:50.198 --> 00:27:51.566
(How could we abandon each other?)

00:27:51.749 --> 00:27:55.787
(But no one wants to be Jumbo's partner.)

00:27:57.297 --> 00:27:58.918
You're still too young.

00:27:59.596 --> 00:28:02.111
When you grow up,
you'll get to date too.

00:28:03.699 --> 00:28:07.718
For now, you can be
Papa and Dad's little kid.

00:28:08.082 --> 00:28:12.097
(Jumbo's sorry. Jumbo will behave now.)

00:28:12.331 --> 00:28:13.719
We love you, Jumbo.

00:28:14.806 --> 00:28:15.814
That's my good boy.

00:28:17.268 --> 00:28:20.394
Lynx, Jumbo said he's sorry.

00:28:21.287 --> 00:28:22.795
He said he won't be like that again.

00:28:26.273 --> 00:28:27.323
How did you know?

00:28:27.919 --> 00:28:30.711
You said it like you could talk to cats.

00:28:40.884 --> 00:28:41.884
Lynx,

00:28:43.803 --> 00:28:44.903
if I tell you this,

00:28:46.712 --> 00:28:47.812
don't be surprised.

00:28:55.501 --> 00:28:56.501
I…

00:29:04.189 --> 00:29:05.189
I know now

00:29:07.193 --> 00:29:08.923
how to make my mom understand us.

00:29:28.574 --> 00:29:29.574
Hey, Tiger.

00:29:30.942 --> 00:29:31.952
What's the rush, son?

00:29:32.069 --> 00:29:33.442
Come have breakfast with us first.

00:29:46.039 --> 00:29:47.141
See?

00:29:47.351 --> 00:29:49.394
You're always avoiding your mom.

00:29:49.578 --> 00:29:51.582
That's why she didn't
prepare you breakfast.

00:29:51.804 --> 00:29:52.998
Where did you get that from?

00:29:53.325 --> 00:29:55.217
I'm not mean, unlike you.

00:29:56.694 --> 00:29:58.226
I make breakfast for you every day.

00:29:59.107 --> 00:30:00.122
Sit down.

00:30:13.658 --> 00:30:14.682
Thank you, Ma.

00:30:30.930 --> 00:30:31.930
Ma,

00:30:35.246 --> 00:30:36.317
are you free today?

00:30:37.251 --> 00:30:38.915
Yes, what's up?

00:30:43.810 --> 00:30:45.403
Do you want to meet my partner?

00:30:59.426 --> 00:31:00.923
Good morning.

00:31:02.126 --> 00:31:04.724
This is Lynx, my boyfriend.

00:31:09.782 --> 00:31:10.888
I'm sorry

00:31:11.586 --> 00:31:13.701
for not being honest with you earlier.

00:31:13.950 --> 00:31:14.950
It's okay.

00:31:15.686 --> 00:31:18.520
I understand you all did it
because you were worried about me.

00:31:23.700 --> 00:31:24.700
Ma,

00:31:25.995 --> 00:31:27.797
it's not just Lynx and me here.

00:31:29.800 --> 00:31:31.202
Our kids are here too.

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:38.960
Aww.

00:31:45.527 --> 00:31:47.092
But don't worry about me, Ma.

00:31:47.906 --> 00:31:50.914
Lynx is the one who
gets his hands on the cats.

00:31:51.966 --> 00:31:54.503
I'm in charge of the heavy work.

00:31:57.009 --> 00:32:00.053
We'll take the best care of our kids.

00:32:13.280 --> 00:32:16.418
With that appetite, you've got
enough energy to run all day.

00:32:18.472 --> 00:32:21.005
Take it easy there. I know it's yummy.

00:32:21.449 --> 00:32:24.003
Slow down.
No one's stealing that from you.

00:32:30.907 --> 00:32:33.795
This is Meow Meow Rice,
our café's signature dish.

00:32:34.709 --> 00:32:36.518
Tiger actually improved the recipe himself.

00:32:38.417 --> 00:32:39.417
Hey, Jumbo.

00:32:39.926 --> 00:32:41.374
Did you just dig through the trash?

00:32:43.981 --> 00:32:45.113
Come here.

00:32:45.592 --> 00:32:47.122
Don't scold him.

00:32:49.111 --> 00:32:51.218
He just wanted to bring a gift to his dads.

00:32:51.608 --> 00:32:52.612
Right?

00:32:52.738 --> 00:32:54.086
He just played with it this morning.

00:32:54.110 --> 00:32:55.543
Right?

00:33:01.913 --> 00:33:02.913
Jumbo.

00:33:03.396 --> 00:33:04.396
Jumbo.

00:33:11.393 --> 00:33:12.393
Ma.

00:33:15.428 --> 00:33:17.300
Jumbo loves the gift you bought for him.

00:33:17.478 --> 00:33:18.823
He keeps wearing it all the time.

00:33:25.982 --> 00:33:29.751
All this time,
I just wanted to see you happy.

00:33:31.109 --> 00:33:32.506
And today, I finally did.

00:33:39.593 --> 00:33:41.518
Do you want to hold him too?

00:34:00.626 --> 00:34:02.066
Papa, hello, Papa.

00:34:06.195 --> 00:34:07.616
Jumbo, thank you so much.

00:34:07.978 --> 00:34:11.677
Thanks to your whisker,

00:34:13.027 --> 00:34:15.514
I finally got to hold my grandchild.

00:34:21.704 --> 00:34:22.704
I knew it.

00:34:22.982 --> 00:34:23.982
Hi.

00:34:24.181 --> 00:34:27.102
You came here to play with
the grandchildren without me.

00:34:27.127 --> 00:34:28.794
Come on, let me.

00:34:28.984 --> 00:34:30.584
Let me hold him too.

00:34:30.619 --> 00:34:32.384
No, I'm not done yet.

00:34:32.880 --> 00:34:33.880
Again?

00:34:34.158 --> 00:34:36.524
You said the same thing
when you were holding baby Tiger.

00:34:36.593 --> 00:34:37.736
When will I get my turn?

00:34:37.767 --> 00:34:39.341
Not yet.

00:34:39.448 --> 00:34:41.127
You still want to be with me, right?

00:34:41.197 --> 00:34:42.356
Come on, let me hold him too.

00:34:42.380 --> 00:34:43.342
No.

00:34:43.367 --> 00:34:44.324
- Just a little.
- No, I won't let you.

00:34:44.350 --> 00:34:45.620
- Just a little.
- No.

00:34:45.778 --> 00:34:46.762
His fur is cute.

00:34:46.787 --> 00:34:48.042
No, you can't.

00:34:48.128 --> 00:34:49.248
- Come on.
- Hold me instead.

00:34:49.325 --> 00:34:50.156
Hold me first.

00:34:50.181 --> 00:34:50.987
No.

00:34:51.012 --> 00:34:52.012
Noooo!

00:35:02.184 --> 00:35:03.516
Here's what you asked me to get.

00:35:04.263 --> 00:35:04.955
Here.

00:35:04.980 --> 00:35:05.980
Thank you.

00:35:06.231 --> 00:35:09.481
Fish maw soup.
It's my grandma's recipe.

00:35:09.694 --> 00:35:10.600
Thank you, Ma.

00:35:10.698 --> 00:35:14.211
Thank you, Lynx, so much
for taking care of my grandchildren.

00:35:14.428 --> 00:35:15.517
It must be exhausting.

00:35:18.426 --> 00:35:20.670
When you have time,
come have a meal with us again.

00:35:20.902 --> 00:35:21.906
I will, Pa.

00:35:23.391 --> 00:35:26.512
You two should get going now.
Get home safely.

00:35:26.574 --> 00:35:27.711
Okay.

00:35:27.961 --> 00:35:29.394
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

00:35:48.133 --> 00:35:49.993
You said you could talk to cats.

00:35:52.583 --> 00:35:53.615
What does that mean?

00:35:58.633 --> 00:36:01.201
Lynx, if I told you

00:36:03.050 --> 00:36:04.617
I've got the power to talk to cats,

00:36:06.174 --> 00:36:07.215
would you believe me?

00:36:12.289 --> 00:36:13.311
What do you mean?

00:36:20.554 --> 00:36:21.554
Everyone,

00:36:23.113 --> 00:36:24.614
it's time to tell him the truth.

00:36:31.089 --> 00:36:32.617
I got this power from your mom.

00:36:36.000 --> 00:36:37.000
Mom?

00:36:42.892 --> 00:36:46.386
Then when I saw her talking to cats…

00:36:53.004 --> 00:36:57.720
This power has been passed down
in your family.

00:36:59.952 --> 00:37:03.394
I believe your mom
wanted to pass it on to you.

00:37:04.490 --> 00:37:07.798
But I happened to be
the last person who was with her.

00:37:10.922 --> 00:37:12.216
I've always wanted to tell you.

00:37:13.859 --> 00:37:15.408
But for this power to work,

00:37:17.092 --> 00:37:18.503
you have to truly love cats.

00:37:20.590 --> 00:37:23.902
And today, I think you're ready.

00:37:35.820 --> 00:37:36.860
I'm not sure.

00:37:42.504 --> 00:37:44.025
I've been watching you.

00:37:45.235 --> 00:37:48.494
You've changed a lot
since the day we first met.

00:37:49.864 --> 00:37:51.292
I think you're ready now

00:37:53.161 --> 00:37:54.601
to take this power

00:37:56.214 --> 00:37:58.997
to take care of the cats
the way your mom did.

00:38:22.334 --> 00:38:23.334
Meow.

00:38:34.802 --> 00:38:37.796
Granny Juu, Lynx can hear everyone now.

00:38:40.534 --> 00:38:41.606
Say something to him.

00:38:41.807 --> 00:38:44.365
Meow~

00:38:51.076 --> 00:38:54.521
Why do I still only hear "Meow"?

00:38:55.501 --> 00:38:57.210
You didn't hear what Granny Juu just said?

00:38:59.347 --> 00:39:00.410
What did she say?

00:39:08.372 --> 00:39:09.523
She said…

00:39:14.343 --> 00:39:15.948
she just remembered something important.

00:39:16.460 --> 00:39:20.118
(And have you decided
who you'll pass it on to?)

00:39:22.844 --> 00:39:26.706
But if I had to pass it on,
it'd have to be…

00:39:32.441 --> 00:39:33.441
Leo.

00:39:37.870 --> 00:39:40.321
Leo should take care of this café after me.

00:39:42.176 --> 00:39:43.307
He's the most suitable one.

00:39:46.059 --> 00:39:47.087
I understand now.

00:39:48.321 --> 00:39:50.608
You choose, Mom.
Do you want to live with the cats or me?

00:39:54.290 --> 00:39:56.260
So in the end,
I was never the one you chose, Mom.

00:40:22.652 --> 00:40:24.188
What are you doing, Tiger?

00:40:24.912 --> 00:40:27.312
Someone abandoned a cat here, Ma.

00:40:27.539 --> 00:40:28.978
No, Tiger.

00:40:29.162 --> 00:40:31.596
Didn't I tell you
not to play with cats anymore?

00:40:31.898 --> 00:40:33.986
Come on.
Let's go inside and put in your eye drops.

00:40:34.196 --> 00:40:35.196
Come on.

00:40:50.401 --> 00:40:52.001
Lynx, where are you?

00:40:52.672 --> 00:40:53.672
Here, Mom.

00:40:55.340 --> 00:40:56.740
I'm heading to work now.

00:40:56.801 --> 00:40:57.801
Alright.

00:40:58.056 --> 00:40:59.514
I put some snacks in the fridge.

00:40:59.597 --> 00:41:00.275
Got it.

00:41:00.300 --> 00:41:01.863
Call me right away if anything happens.

00:41:01.930 --> 00:41:02.738
Okay, Mom.

00:41:02.763 --> 00:41:03.763
Come here.

00:41:04.429 --> 00:41:05.549
This side too.

00:41:07.586 --> 00:41:09.275
Give me a hug too.

00:41:09.500 --> 00:41:10.595
I'll be home soon.

00:41:10.646 --> 00:41:11.646
Okay!

00:41:12.467 --> 00:41:13.614
Call me if anything, okay?

00:41:17.543 --> 00:41:18.543
Bye.

00:41:38.010 --> 00:41:39.010
Hm?

00:41:54.467 --> 00:41:55.467
Meow.

00:42:03.865 --> 00:42:04.924
Whose cat is this?

00:42:05.463 --> 00:42:07.117
It got abandoned.

00:42:07.567 --> 00:42:09.398
Can I keep it?

00:42:17.484 --> 00:42:18.416
(Next Episode)
What's this about?

00:42:18.441 --> 00:42:19.441
We just found out

00:42:19.487 --> 00:42:21.567
that Je Meow intended to
hand this café over to you.

00:42:21.729 --> 00:42:24.676
That day, I thought I made my mom proud.

00:42:25.427 --> 00:42:27.762
The truth is, she had probably
stopped waiting for me a long time ago.

00:42:27.786 --> 00:42:29.306
I already passed on the power to Lynx.

00:42:29.336 --> 00:42:30.896
But I don't know why Lynx
still cannot hear cats talking.

00:42:30.920 --> 00:42:33.390
What Lynx has been through is complicated.

00:42:33.912 --> 00:42:35.712
Him living with the cats right now,

00:42:36.305 --> 00:42:37.418
I don't know if it's because he loves them,

00:42:37.442 --> 00:42:39.082
or because he feels guilty about his mom.

00:42:39.294 --> 00:42:40.294
Mom.

00:42:41.630 --> 00:42:42.642
Do you love me?